snippet.title: CONFRIMED: Amber Heard remains in DCEU
snippet.description:
Mikey Sutton has confirmed (per Deadline) that WarnerMedia has decided to NOT fire Amber Heard as Mera from AQUAMAN 2 & the DCEU. This of course comes after the very public divorce from her former husband Johnny Depp, and his defamation lawsuit against The Sun in the UK. I figured she wouldn't be fired, however I am glad that WarnerMedia is staying out of Cancel Culture entirely.
